{"word":"στήκω","slug":"στήκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>στήϰω</el></b> [<el>ἵστημι</el> via the perf. <el>ἕστηϰα</el>] <b>stand,</b> of a position that is up or erect <b><a href='B:480 3:31'>Mk 3:31</a>; <a href='B:480 11:25'>11:25</a>; <a href='B:500 1:26'>J 1:26</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>;</b> in imagery, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on stability <b><a href='B:500 8:44'>J 8:44</a>; <a href='B:520 14:4'>Ro 14:4</a>; <a href='B:530 16:13'>1 Cor 16:13</a>; <a href='B:550 5:1'>Gal 5:1</a>; <a href='B:570 1:27'>Phil 1:27</a>; <a href='B:570 4:1'>4:1</a>; <a href='B:590 3:8'>1 Th 3:8</a>; <a href='B:600 2:15'>2 Th 2:15</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:στῆθος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:στῆναι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}